                                    tnum_const(val));
    break;
```
- This case performs bitwise operations (`tnum_and` and `tnum_or`) on the registers' `var_off`.
- There is no explicit marking of the registers as having known values after these operations.

#### Cases: `BPF_JGE`, `BPF_JGT`, `BPF_JLE`, `BPF_JLT`, `BPF_JSLE`, `BPF_JSLT`
These cases involve comparisons and updating the `umin_value`, `umax_value`, `smin_value`, and `smax_value` of the registers based on the comparison results.
- There is no explicit marking of the registers as having known values after these operations.

